  • java.lang.Object
    • org.flossware.jcore.AbstractCommonBase
      • org.solenopsis.keraiai.soap.security.AbstractSecurityMgr<P>
  • Type Parameters:
    P - The type of port for login/logout.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    SecurityMgr
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    EnterpriseSecurityMgr, PartnerSecurityMgr, ToolingSecurityMgr

    public abstract class AbstractSecurityMgr<P>
extends org.flossware.jcore.AbstractCommonBase
implements SecurityMgr
    Represents a way to login and out of SFDC. Can be used to abstract out the enterprise, partner and tooling web services.
    Author:
    Scot P. Floess
